titles.title: A concurrent resolution to correct technical errors in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 2333.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Mr. Hamilton asked unanimous consent to take from the Speaker's table and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 4/26/1994--Introduced. Makes technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 2333 (authorizing appropriations for the Department of State, the United States Information Agency, and related agencies).
